org.wallerlab.yoink.cube.domain

Class SimpleCube

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wallerlab.yoink.cube.domain.SimpleCube
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cube

    @Component
public class SimpleCube
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cube
    Cube domain Model stores all information about cube. Constructing a cube needs the coordinate of the origin grid point, number of steps along x/y/z axis, and also step size along x/y/z axis.
